\subtree{
\title{Cost Optimizations Available}
\pre{\startverb
| Strategy | Savings | Notes |
|----------|---------|-------|
| **Prompt Caching** | Up to 90% | For repeated system prompts |
| **Batch API** | 50% | Async processing |
| **Rush Mode** | ~80% | Haiku vs Opus |
| **Token Optimization** | Variable | Concise prompts |
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Amp Pricing Pass-Through}
\p{Amp passes LLM costs directly with \strong{no markup} for individuals/teams.}

\ul{
\li{\startverb **Free tier**: $10/day grant (all modes including Opus 4.5)\stopverb}
\li{\startverb **Enterprise**: +50% over individual/team rates\stopverb}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Example Cost Calculation}
\p{Typical thread (~50 messages, 100K tokens total):}

\pre{\startverb
Opus 4.5: ~$1.50/thread (50K in × $5 + 50K out × $25)
Haiku 4.5: ~$0.30/thread (80% savings)
Gemini 3 Pro: ~$0.70/thread (mid-tier)
\stopverb}
}
}

